{"tid":1468109,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［抗爭公約］三大基本原則，請聽君一言","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:25.000Z","uid":167192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7e620373727fc3db555505661b202c574c729c","tid":1468109,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:25.000Z","msg":"今日機場事件嘅好壞不需評論，成個反送中、乃至到反政府嘅運動可以去到呢步，全靠大家一齊努力，無大台、兄弟爬山。<br />\n<br />\n但係反思、檢討同進步係一定要有，有幾點希望大家可以一齊諗下係咪應該注意一下。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 絕不阻撓醫療人員工作</span></span><br />\n醫護界人士為運動發聲、靜坐抗議，係因為死黑警濫暴，同埋多次企圖阻礙救援工作，有違人道原則。對於醫護朋友黎講，不論藍黃黑白，只要係傷者，都應該有接受治療嘅權利。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係黑警，我地恥與為伍。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n被人口實之餘，請諗下對唔對得住支持我地咁耐嘅醫護人員手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 盡一切能力保護記者</span></span><br />\n記者嘅角色唔需要多講，就係將最真實嘅畫面呈現比普羅大眾。<br />\n頭先立場哥哥係混亂中不停受到推撞，並且被黑警嘅胡椒噴霧擊中，眼睛同皮膚紅晒。<br />\n但係由於現場一波未平，一波又起，立場哥哥連清洗\b嘅時間都無，就已經趕去人群堆入面。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔駛多，幫一幫真係會差好遠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 不分化、不割席、不篤灰</span></span><br />\n成場運動嘅基石<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請謹記，矛頭一致，五大訴求缺一不可</span></span><br />\n所有抗爭嘅同路人，不論年齡、男女、方法，都係有同一理念嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人，一定得！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d17692d7233c061e3703b677281b58168f814b03","tid":1468109,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27eaf6dfcc0e9947aea57b03d82ce72fdc01f2db","tid":1468109,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6536aa04272dae411170bd752258d4ddd22a1c59","tid":1468109,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"34308cb69f0566f018b1b04a34045d547acb1ab6","tid":1468109,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OHK9X4q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOHK9X4q.jpg&h=0e2f1512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b0d7771791a9f14c36027cdbad475196ceaa30c","tid":1468109,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:25.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}